name: 3DS case - Sweets Deco
description: -Original design by Atelier Lolita- Acrylic 3DS hard case adorned with fake whipped cream, cute sweets, jewels, and pearls. Camera lens, headphone jacks and all buttons are all accessible. Hand-crafted with love. Each product at Atelier Lolita is hand crafted individually so you can smile knowing there is only one of these in the world. Disclaimer: Only for the 3DS. will not fit on DSi, DS light or original DS. Not edible, not recommended for children under 6 years of age - small parts. 17/02/2011 update - We have found a very slight yellow discolouration due to the oxidation of the resin glue used, even though the glue stated that it "dies clear". We at Atelier Lolita believe in honesty and quality, hence truthfully reported the issue and is subsequently lowering the price. We will discontinue the use of the glue in future works and have sourced a glue specifically suited to rhinestones. We apologise for any inconvenience caused.
